snippet: Col. Carl Jones, the No. 2 commander of the 90th Missile Wing at F. E. Warren Air Force Base, Wyo., was dismissed for “a loss of trust and confidence in his leadership abilities,” and has been reassigned.
abstract: Air Force fires two nuclear commanders and disciplines third; Col Carl Jones, the No 2 commander of the 90th Missile Wing at F E Warren Air Force Base, Wyo, is dismissed for 'a loss of trust and confidence in his leadership abilities,' and is reassigned.
